@startuml
title Fortuna - System Context

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Klient" as Customer

rectangle "Frontend\nReact + Vite" as Frontend
rectangle "Bruno Collection\nAPI manual tests" as Bruno

package "Backend" {
  rectangle "Fortuna.Api\nASP.NET Core" as Api
  rectangle "Fortuna.Application\nUse Cases / CQRS Handlers" as App
  rectangle "Fortuna.Domain\nDomain Model" as Domain
  rectangle "Fortuna.Infrastructure\nEF Core + JWT + Repositories" as Infra
  rectangle "Fortuna.ReadModel\nDashboard projections" as ReadModel
}

database "FortunaWriteDb" as WriteDb
database "FortunaReadDb" as ReadDb

Customer --> Frontend : register / login /\ndashboard / transfer
Customer --> Bruno : invoke requests

Frontend --> Api : HTTPS JSON API
Bruno --> Api : HTTPS JSON API

Api --> App : commands / queries
Api --> ReadModel : dashboard query
App --> Domain : business rules
App --> Infra : repositories,\nunit of work,\npassword hashing,\nJWT

Infra --> WriteDb : transactional writes
Infra --> ReadModel : outbox source
ReadModel --> ReadDb : projections / queries
ReadModel --> WriteDb : read OutboxMessages

note right of ReadModel
  Dashboard is served from a separate
  read database populated asynchronously
  from outbox events.
end note

@enduml
